            <title><![CDATA[💬👤 #求实处: 🔗 红海断绝 做事不声明，全都是狠人]]></title>
            <link><![CDATA[http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkxMzIyNjE0OA==&amp;amp;mid=2247496640&amp;amp;idx=1&amp;amp;sn=a6158427fb07796351655e2369cc4489&amp;amp;chksm=c0bea438bce8434ec804e6ebd460966f6962671b7d72bcadab6f45a8413d6bb943a221ac8641&amp;amp;scene=0&amp;amp;xtrack=1#rd]]></link>
            <description><![CDATA[<div id="page-content" class="rich_media_area_primary">      <div class="rich_media_area_primary_inner">                                                        <div id="img-content" class="rich_media_wrp">                    <h1 class="rich_media_title " id="activity-name">            红海断绝          </h1>          <div id="meta_content" class="rich_media_meta_list">                                      <span id="copyright_logo" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta icon_appmsg_tag appmsg_title_tag weui-wa-hotarea">原创</span>                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text">                                                                                    <span role="link" tabindex="0" id="js_author_name" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight rich_media_meta_link weui-wa-hotarea" datarewardsn="" datatimestamp="" datacanreward="0">叶立华</span>                                                                            </span>                                                                                                      <span class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_nickname" id="profileBt">              <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="wx_tap_link js_wx_tap_highlight weui-wa-hotarea" id="js_name">                求实处              </a>              <div id="js_profile_qrcode" aria-hidden="true" class="profile_container" style="display:none;">                <div class="profile_inner">                  <strong class="profile_nickname">求实处</strong>                  <img class="profile_avatar" id="js_profile_qrcode_img" src="" alt="">                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">微信号</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">QIUSHICHU-</span>                  </p>                  <p class="profile_meta">                  <label class="profile_meta_label">功能介绍</label>                  <span class="profile_meta_value">讲政治，靠得住，没有关系低保户</span>                  </p>                </div>                <span class="profile_arrow_wrp" id="js_profile_arrow_wrp">                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_out"></i>                  <i class="profile_arrow arrow_in"></i>                </span>              </div>            </span>            <span id="meta_content_hide_info">              <em id="publish_time" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text"></em>              <em id="js_ip_wording_wrp" class="rich_media_meta rich_media_meta_text" role="option" aria-labelledby="js_a11y_op_ip_wording js_ip_wording" style="display: none;"><span id="js_a11y_op_ip_wording" aria-hidden="true">发表于</span><span aria-hidden="true" id="js_ip_wording"></span></em>                          </span>          </div>                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  <div class="rich_media_content js_underline_content                       defaultNoSetting            " id="js_content" style="visibility: hidden;"><section style="text-align: center;padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><img class="rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg" data-imgfileid="100012987" data-ratio="0.9537037037037037" data-s="300,640" data-src="https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hr6mUjEf2jaaeUdTEjRmqazPMg5Oc6TyfIBia3HicJK8a2cnEqh8dYaHsHIkQiaXl5yVcONVLW1UhicpRJPhqeNhJA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&amp;from=appmsg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="1080" style=""></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><br></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">1981年，苏联举行西方-81军演。规模庞大，演习逼真，举世震惊。西方的参谋部普遍推演，苏军照此进度，一周就到了巴黎。<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">1983年，北约两年磨一剑，进行了对等演习。叫做神射手-83。<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">但是，正常军演都是军队自己演习，这次演习，北约把西欧各国政府的要员都叫了进来，既然地面部队无法对抗苏军的西方-81，大家就演习对苏联进行核打击的决策流程吧。<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">于是，演习前，美军将战备等级直接升级到比古巴导弹危机还强的最高级。模拟的是核战爆发后的军事行动，英国首相撒切尔夫人亲手按下了用于演习的核按钮。<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">但是这次演习前有一个问题，就是北约没有事先通知苏联。<p></p></span></strong></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><br></span></strong></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">在苏联看来，北约的动向是英国首相撒切尔夫人准备配合美国使用核弹，美军将战备等级提升至核战爆发。大量中程导弹发射车进入战备，北约的加密通讯数量暴涨。<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">那么，苏联首脑怎么判断美国人是不是要打核战争呢？<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">无法判断。<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">事情做到哪一步截止，要提前声明。提</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 12pt;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">前不声明，动向总是逃不过对面的间谍。就像是犯罪，必然有痕迹</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 12pt;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">。</span><strong style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 12pt;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">1941年，德军入侵苏联之前，无线电通讯的数量也暴涨过。</span></strong></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><strong style="font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size: 12pt;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><span lang="EN-US" style="font-size: 12pt;color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><br></span></strong></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">于是，对面一定会按照最高等级进行布防。擦枪走火只在一瞬间。<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;">以色列要做什么，打到哪里结束，船到底送的是什么，如果不想要周围国家都参与进来，要提前声明。<p></p></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><br></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;"><strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12pt;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: rgb(192, 0, 0);">以色列没有提前声明，那么，属于中欧铁路班列的时代就来了。<p></p></span></strong></span></section><section style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><br></section><section class="mp_profile_iframe_wrp" style="padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;"><mp-common-profile class="js_uneditable custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe" data-pluginname="mpprofile" data-id="MzkxMzIyNjE0OA==" data-headimg="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/hr6mUjEf2jaBeibcpNMyh5WEgHyQk6Sqp6GDWEr5WvfsASPPKNvqjSGeE7mandCjSocE7sfc9P6VQwIUjRuH5bQ/0?wx_fmt=png" data-nickname="求实处" data-alias="QIUSHICHU-" data-signature="讲政治，靠得住，没有关系低保户" data-from="0" data-is_biz_ban="0"></mp-common-profile></section><section style="display: none;padding-left: 1em;padding-right: 1em;line-height: 2em;"><br></section><p style="display: none;"><mp-style-type data-value="10000"></mp-style-type></p></div>          <script type="text/javascript" nonce="1813049290" reportloaderror>            var first_sceen__time = (+new Date());            if ("" == 1 && document.getElementById('js_content')) {              document.getElementById('js_content').addEventListener("selectstart",function(e){ e.preventDefault(); });            }          </script>        </div>                        <div id="js_tags_preview_toast" class="article-tag__error-tips" style="display: none;">预览时标签不可点</div>                        <div id="content_bottom_area" class="rich_media_tool_area"></div>                              </div>    </div>]]></description>
